node.text:
Surfing with the little one 🏄‍♂️ Tag someone who should see this!

🎶: Wish You Were Here by @vicetone & @willimmusic (feat. Wink XY)

📽 @billykemper

This is #Greece! 1-10, which one was your favorite? 👇We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @explorerfervor 

1. Saint Luxury Suites, Santorini 
2. Bill & Coo Suites and Lounge, Mykonos
3. Cavo Tagoo Mykonos
4. Canaves Oia Suites, Santorini
5. Villa Bordeaux Santorini
6. Canaves Oia Suites, Santorini
7. Mykonos
8. Cavo Tagoo Santorini
9. Saint Luxury Suites, Santorini
10. Katikies Santorini

📽 @momentsofgregory

node.text:
Yoga and Meditation with Guru Turtle 🧘🏼‍♂️Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @explorerfervor 

This unique type of meditation is all about relaxation and being one with the ocean 🌿😄

The Great Barrier Reef in the Australian estate of Queensland is home to six out of seven of the world's sea turtle species. Not only this coast is radiant with sunshine, but its picturesque landscapes are also overflowing with an impressive population of native animals.

From witnessing baby turtles make their way to the sea to see adult turtles enjoying @nature, that's a magical sight to behold.

Tag your @nature lovers friends! 🐢

📽 @jacintashackleton
📍 Queensland, Australia
🎶 Arnaud Gauthier - Yoga
